						"title": "Explore industry-specific use cases for GenAI",
						"titleSize": null,
						"subtitle": null,
						"subtitleSize": null,
						"copy": "Generative AI (GenAI) has tremendous potential for reshaping industries. \n\n- __Financial services__ firms can deliver personalized investment recommendations.\n- __Healthcare providers__ can enhance operational efficiency.\n- __Retailers__ can streamline creation of targeted marketing content. \n- __Manufacturers__ can help ensure machines stay up and running.\n- __Gaming studios__ can produce more immersive experiences.\n\nAnd that's just the beginning. \n\nTo make the most of GenAI and reduce potential risks, your organization needs a strategic approach — one that focuses on the right use cases and avoids haphazard adoption of AI tools. \n\nCheck out the infographic for a few ways organizations in multiple industries are using GenAI. For help finding the best, most impactful GenAI use cases for your company, contact developers@cloudflare.com.\n",
